Description:
Introducing the **Maybelline New York Tattoo Brow 3-Day Styling Gel**, your secret to effortlessly defined and stunningly natural eyebrows that wow! This innovative, semi-permanent tinted eyebrow gel is designed for easy application and long-lasting wear. Say goodbye to smudges and fading; this waterproof formula is smudge-proof and climate-proof, ensuring your brows look flawless all day, every day. The unique two-way mini brush makes shaping and defining your brows simpler than ever before, giving you a natural makeup look that truly lasts. Achieve beautiful, fuller-looking brows for up to 3 days with this incredible formula, available in 3 versatile shades.
